# Teebot Flow Module Isolation Rule

- Respect build order: Inventory -> Customers -> Delivery Challan.
- Keep backend logic isolated in domain modules under `src-tauri/src/modules/`.
- Do not mix frontend view logic with Rust business rules.
- SQLite writes and validation for business entities must stay in Rust commands.
- For cross-module behavior, use shared helpers only (db init, shared types), not direct module coupling.
